item.title: CVE-2017-20134|2024-08-05T21:45:25.971Z -- itech -- freelancer%20script
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as critical, has been found in Itech Freelancer Script 5.13. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality of the file /category.php. The manipulation of the argument sk leads to sql injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
